title: X-Campus (01 - 04)  (2010) (Minutemen-Meganubis)
description:
X-Campus (01 - 04)  (2010) (Minutemen-Meganubis)


In a world that fears and hates them two groups of mutant teens must hide amongst there fellow peers. The new first year students Anna, Scott, Bobby, Ororo and Hank come to Worthington Foundation for a new semester to find that a war has brewing among normal baseline humans and mutants. Professors Magnus and Xavier sway as many students as they can to their causes. But what if the war is already at end game? What happens when you can't trust any of the other teachers? What is Project Mastermold?
